us board of governors for five years before being appointed chancellor in   giardini holds a ba in economics from sfu llb from ubc and llm from cambridge university trinity hall she has been married to tony giardini for  years and they have three grown children click here to go to the chancellors website simon fraser university is consistently ranked among canadas top comprehensive universities and is one of the top  universities in the world under  years old guided by a vision to be canadas leading engaged university sfu engages actively with the community in its research and teaching across three campuses in vancouver burnaby and surrey anne giardini on twitter england’s mental health experiment nocost talk therapy  the new york times httpstcobwglixht skip to content home home home current page moments moments moments current page search query search twitter saved searches remove in this conversation verified accountprotected tweets  suggested users verified accountprotected tweets  verified accountprotected tweets  language english bahasa indonesia bahasa melayu català čeština dansk deutsch english uk español filipino français hrvatski italiano magyar nederlands norsk polski português română slovenčina suomi svenska tiếng việt türkçe ελληνικά български език русский српски українська мова עִבְרִית العربية فارسی मराठी हिन्दी বাংলা ગુજરાતી தமிழ் ಕನ್ನಡ ภาษาไทย 한국어    have an account log in have an account remember me · forgot password new to twitter sign up aegiardinis profile anne giardini aegiardini tweets anne giardini aegiardini director writer chancellor of sfu vancouver canada writersunioncamemberannegi… joined december  tweets   twitter about help center terms privacy policy cookies ads info dismiss close previous next close go to a persons profile saved searches remove in this conversation verified accountprotected tweets  suggested users verified accountprotected tweets  verified accountprotected tweets  close promote this tweet close block cancel block add 